{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"boolean","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/boolean","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">XSLT/XPath リファレンス</a></b>: <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">XSLT 要素</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/EXSLT\">EXSLT 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">XPath 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath 軸</a>\n</div>\n<p><code>boolean</code> 関数は式を評価し、 true または false を返します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"構文","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">boolean( expression )\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"引数","title":"引数","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"expression\"><code>expression</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>評価される式です。式は論理値のほか、数値やノード集合を参照することができます。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返値","title":"返値","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>expression</code> を評価した結果から得られる論理値 <code>true</code> または <code>false</code>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"メモ","title":"メモ","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>数値は、正のゼロ、負のゼロ、 <code>NaN</code> の場合は false と評価されます。それ以外の場合は true と評価されます。</li>\n  <li>ノード集合は、空集合でなければ true と評価されます。</li>\n  <li>文字列は、空文字列ならば false と評価されます。そうでなければ true と評価されます。</li>\n  <li>4 つの基本型以外の型のオブジェクトは、その型に応じた方法で論理値に変換されます。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"定義","title":"定義","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/xpath#function-boolean\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">XPath 1.0 4.3</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko_の対応","title":"Gecko の対応","isH3":false,"content":"<p>対応済み。</p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"構文"},{"text":"引数","id":"引数"},{"text":"返値","id":"返値"},{"text":"メモ","id":"メモ"},{"text":"定義","id":"定義"},{"text":"Gecko の対応","id":"gecko_の対応"}],"summary":"boolean 関数は式を評価し、 true または false を返します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"boolean","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"boolean","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"boolean","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/xpath/functions/boolean","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/xpath/functions/boolean/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath","title":"XPath"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions","title":"Functions"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/boolean","title":"boolean"}],"pageTitle":"boolean - XPath | MDN","noIndexing":false}}